Klasse Parser.Expression.Binary

java.lang.Object
de.happybavarian07.coolstufflib.languagemanager.expressionengine.Parser.Expression
de.happybavarian07.coolstufflib.languagemanager.expressionengine.Parser.Expression.Binary
Umschließende Klasse:
Parser.Expression
public static class Parser.Expression.Binary extends Parser.Expression

Represents a binary operation expression with a left operand, operator, and right operand. Handles mathematical operations (+, -, *, /, %, ^) and comparison operations (==, !=, <, >, <=, >=).


 // Creates: 10 + 5
 Expression expr = new Binary(
     new Literal(10),
     new Token(TokenType.PLUS, "+", null, 1),
     new Literal(5)
 );
